      <h2>Why 0% Down for Construction</h2>

      <p>Construction is cash-intensive. Fuel, wages, materials, rental, permits. Every RM matters.</p>

      <p>RM50,000 down payment = 2 months fuel for fleet. Or 1 month wages. Or materials for small project.</p>

      <p>0% down = Equipment deployed immediately. Cash preserved for operations. Project starts on time.</p>

